title: remove excess and update to ChartJS `2.1.6`
body:
This pull is a start toward an upgrade to ChartJS [`2.1.6`](https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/releases/tag/v2.1.6).  While upgrading, I also cleaned out much of the unnecessary bower remnants.  These remnants get copied, so can slow rendering of the `htmlwidget`.  I also had to make a minor change to `initialize`/`renderValue` to work with the new API.

If you have no interest in upgrading, then please feel free to ignore and close.
